SUMMARY:National Scrabble Day Event
DESCRIPTION:Monday\, April 13\, 1-3pm. GSC. Free. \nJoin us for a celebration of this classic word game. All skill levels welcome. Expect snacks and good company. We’ll have boards and tiles\, but feel free to bring your own as well. RSVP: 206.297.0875. \n 
